  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About This Indie Game</h2> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rosttle is a 2D top-down shooter developed by an individual. In each round, players must survive as long as possible, collect the yellow energy dots scattered on the map, and avoid obstacles. Players must use every available method to defeat monsters, earn coins, and obtain rewards. </p> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Content</h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"> []<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every weapon has a unique passive ability, and different combinations of firearms create distinct playstyles.</p>[/] </ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"> []<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced combat with gradually increasing difficulty.</p>[/] </ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"> []<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is an indie game, and it will receive long-term updates in the future.</p>[/] </ul> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapon Passive Combinations</h2> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game, the passive abilities of items interact with each other. By adjusting the placement of items in your inventory according to their properties, you can achieve a “1+1>2” effect, making your character even more powerful.</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/c26939ee10a60e24997e342dda531d23.poster.avif?t=1742015361\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/c26939ee10a60e24997e342dda531d23.webm?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/c26939ee10a60e24997e342dda531d23.mp4?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Randomly Generated Game Maps</h2> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will enter different rooms, and no matter which path you choose, you will encounter various events. However, the ultimate goal is to reach the highest point.</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/68c6f1cfcedb0dcb277fa388c97dfec0.poster.avif?t=1742015361\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/68c6f1cfcedb0dcb277fa388c97dfec0.webm?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/68c6f1cfcedb0dcb277fa388c97dfec0.mp4?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Round Rewards</h2> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a battle, based on the characteristics of your weapons and the passives already in your inventory, choose a weapon to add to your inventory to enhance your character’s strength and increase the game’s difficulty.</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/0b4b6853e1e3a5e47b74427dfb22a930.poster.avif?t=1742015361\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/0b4b6853e1e3a5e47b74427dfb22a930.webm?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/0b4b6853e1e3a5e47b74427dfb22a930.mp4?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Random Events</h2> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the game, you will encounter various random events that force you to make choices, and every decision you make will affect your character.</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/43f820c9b37d26ebfd1238a439a9e766.poster.avif?t=1742015361\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/43f820c9b37d26ebfd1238a439a9e766.webm?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/43f820c9b37d26ebfd1238a439a9e766.mp4?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About This Indie Game</h2> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rosttle is a 2D top-down shooter developed by an individual. In each round, players must survive as long as possible, collect the yellow energy dots scattered on the map, and avoid obstacles. Players must use every available method to defeat monsters, earn coins, and obtain rewards. </p> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Content</h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"> []<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every weapon has a unique passive ability, and different combinations of firearms create distinct playstyles.</p>[/] </ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"> []<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced combat with gradually increasing difficulty.</p>[/] </ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"> []<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is an indie game, and it will receive long-term updates in the future.</p>[/] </ul> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapon Passive Combinations</h2> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game, the passive abilities of items interact with each other. By adjusting the placement of items in your inventory according to their properties, you can achieve a “1+1>2” effect, making your character even more powerful.</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/c26939ee10a60e24997e342dda531d23.poster.avif?t=1742015361\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/c26939ee10a60e24997e342dda531d23.webm?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/c26939ee10a60e24997e342dda531d23.mp4?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Randomly Generated Game Maps</h2> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will enter different rooms, and no matter which path you choose, you will encounter various events. However, the ultimate goal is to reach the highest point.</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/68c6f1cfcedb0dcb277fa388c97dfec0.poster.avif?t=1742015361\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/68c6f1cfcedb0dcb277fa388c97dfec0.webm?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/68c6f1cfcedb0dcb277fa388c97dfec0.mp4?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Round Rewards</h2> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a battle, based on the characteristics of your weapons and the passives already in your inventory, choose a weapon to add to your inventory to enhance your character’s strength and increase the game’s difficulty.</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/0b4b6853e1e3a5e47b74427dfb22a930.poster.avif?t=1742015361\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/0b4b6853e1e3a5e47b74427dfb22a930.webm?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/0b4b6853e1e3a5e47b74427dfb22a930.mp4?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Random Events</h2> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the game, you will encounter various random events that force you to make choices, and every decision you make will affect your character.</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/43f820c9b37d26ebfd1238a439a9e766.poster.avif?t=1742015361\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/43f820c9b37d26ebfd1238a439a9e766.webm?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205970/extras/43f820c9b37d26ebfd1238a439a9e766.mp4?t=1742015361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
